Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備  向前！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖定敵軍  主炮發射準備！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.35,0:01:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離  800
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.89,0:01:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝填  彈種  榴彈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.96,0:01:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝彈完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.26,0:02:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.72,0:02:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開炮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.67,0:02:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  轉告後方已擊毀敵軍一輛  緊跟上來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.49,0:02:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊毀敵軍一輛嗎  真不賴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還遠遠不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利西婭  是克勞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我們去喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
